OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly fine,
OL,6,Fwith the risk of heavy thundery
OL,7,Fshowers receding in the far east into
OL,8,Fthe evening. Dry overnight with clear
OL,9,Fperiods. Widely humid, very warm in
OL,10,Finland urban areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FPerhaps on the cloudy side at
OL,13,Ffirst in some southern and western
OL,14,Fareas, with a humid feel generally.
OL,15,FBecoming widely hot in developing
OL,16,Fsunny periods, perhaps triggering
OL,17,Fisolated thundery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
